      "raw_text": "The transportation board on the\nNorthern Pacific has made a ruling\nthat any train leaving it's district to\nrun on another branch loses its\nrights. unless special orders have\nbeen given by the head office This\nruling has been modified somewhat\nby Superintendent A. Beamer OF this\ndivision, and 1t is modified to the\nextent that 1t will not apply to trains\nwhen leaving their district and going\nonto the Palouse and Lewiston and\nCentral Washington branches."
